      • select

        public void select​(Taggable taggable)
        Parameters:
        taggable - the taggable element that will be tagged with this select
        Throws:
        WeaponCardException - if the current action is not a select
        WeaponCardException - if you are trying to tag a player but the tag was for a square or a room
        java.lang.ClassCastException - if the select type differs from the class of the taggable object

      • getPlayersToMark

      • getPlayersMoves
